T_{\text{h}} &= 300^{\circ}\text{C}+273.15 = 573.15\ \text{K},\\[4pt]
T_{\text{c}} &=  80^{\circ}\text{C}+273.15 = 353.15\ \text{K}.
\end{aligned}
\]

Thus  

\[
\eta_{\text{Carnot}} = 1-\frac{353.15}{573.15}
                     = \frac{573.15-353.15}{573.15}
